## §1 — ParseMode

HTML is the exclusive parse mode for the entire project. Never use MarkdownV2.
All dynamic data must be wrapped with html.escape() before interpolation.
Required import at the top of any file that builds Telegram messages:

```python
# Required: HTML-safe escaping for all dynamic Telegram content
from html import escape
```

