## §3 — Standard HTML Template

Mandatory message hierarchy (do not deviate):

```
<b>TITLE — Subtitle</b>

<i>optional context line (max 1 line)</i>

message body (max ~600 chars before truncation)

🔗 <a href="URL">Link Label</a>
```

Rules:
- Absolute maximum: **4096 chars** (Telegram hard limit).
- Long dynamic content: truncate at **800 chars** + `…`.
- Never use `<br>` — use `\n` for line breaks.

