## §6 — Wallet Truncation

Fixed display pattern — never show a full address to the user:

```python
# Truncate wallet address for safe display
def truncate_wallet(addr: str) -> str:
    return f"{addr[:6]}…{addr[-4:]}" if len(addr) > 10 else addr
```

